        "title": "JFreeChart not showing XYPlot series axis labels",
        "body": "<p>I am using a <code>XYPlot<\/code> in a <code>TimeSeriesChart<\/code>. I have a <code>dateAxis<\/code> and <code>valueAxis<\/code> (log) for displaying few time series. My issue is I need the end prices of the series on the right-side-axis next to the end of the series. I am not interested for the axis labels, since the same can be approximated on the left. Something similar to the red circle in the attached chart.<\/p>\n<p>What is the best way to do this? I modified a copy of <code>PriceVolumeDemo1.java<\/code> as <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/revisions/76644701/1\">here<\/a>. I tried a few variations, but it's not working. This shows the labels similar to what I want:<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/PrOmn.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/PrOmn.gif\" alt=\"image\" /><\/a><\/p>\n",
